<p><strong>II. PhD Post MS</strong> (108 hours total, including 32 hours transferred from the MS). <strong>Credit for MS Degree</strong>: Those having an MS degree from an accredited institution will be awarded 32 semester hours of credit toward the PhD degree requirement, which includes 24 hours of course work and 8 hours of <span class="sc_courseinline"><a href="/search/?P=IE%20599" title="IE 599" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'IE 599');">IE 599</a></span>.</p>

